00:04:33.079 --> 00:04:38.200
Yeah, so it's when I joined the organization, my first title was assistant director of advanced

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:43.079
analytics. And pretty much everyone thinks that is Moneyball, right? So it's like player

00:04:43.079 --> 00:04:50.519
analytics, it's R&D, it's the book or the movie, if you've seen that. For better or worse, I don't

00:04:50.519 --> 00:04:55.519
really have any direct interaction with our baseball operations team. We've got a fantastic R&D

00:04:55.519 --> 00:05:04.839
