or major league baseball and then to be a coach or a scout or something. For a variety of reasons,

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:15.880
that didn't work out. So I went into the professional workforce fast forward eight or

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:19.960
nine years and I had the opportunity to join the Cubs organization on the business side and it was

00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:25.559
sort of the perfect marriage of what I had spent being incredibly passionate about for the first

